OL,3,CEx-patient of Michael Watt to receive
OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,FA former patient of Belfast
OL,7,Fneurologist Michael Watt is to receive
OL,8,F#50,000 in damages for her "appalling
OL,9,Fstandard of care", a High Court judge
OL,10,Fruled today.
OL,12,FMr Justice Colton awarded the payout
OL,13,Fto Martine Norney to cover psychiatric
OL,14,Fand medical injuries during
OL,15,Fconsultation and treatment by the ex-
OL,16,Fdoctor.
