OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,FThe Belfast Health and Social Care
OL,7,FTrust was also held jointly liable in
OL,8,Fher negligence claim over a procedure
OL,9,Fcarried out for a neurological
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FWith both defendants ordered to pay
OL,13,Fhalf the damages each, Mr Justice
OL,14,FColon stated: "It is trite to say that
OL,15,Fthe conduct of (Mr Watt) was
OL,16,Fappalling. This would be clear to any
OL,17,Flay person."
