OL,6,FThe medic, who worked at the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Hospital in Belfast, was at
OL,8,Fthe centre of Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fbiggest-ever patient recall in 2018.
OL,11,FThousands of people were re-examined
OL,12,Famid concerns about the treatment they
OL,13,Freceived from him.
OL,15,FHe was struck off the medical register
OL,16,Flast year after his professional
OL,17,Fperformance was found to be
OL,18,Funacceptably low.
