OL,3,CEx-patient of Michael Watt to receive
OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,FMs Norney sued both the neurologist
OL,7,Fand the Trust for alleged grossly
OL,8,Fsubstandard medical care after she
OL,9,Fbegan to experience headaches,
OL,10,Fdizziness and nausea along with pins
OL,11,Fand needles in her right arm and
OL,12,Fsensitivity to light and sound.
OL,14,FThe court heard she was initially
OL,15,Freferred to the neurology clinic at
OL,16,Fthe Royal before seeking a private
OL,17,Fconsultation with Watt in July 2016.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
