OL,3,CEx-patient of Michael Watt to receive
OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,FHe told her she had a spinal leak and
OL,7,Fthat he would arrange an epidural
OL,8,Fblood patch to be carried out under
OL,9,Fthe NHS rather than privately.
OL,11,FThe procedure involves taking blood
OL,12,Ffrom her arm and injecting it into the
OL,13,Fback, to close the hole and "cure the
OL,14,Fheadaches".
OL,16,FMs Norney was also informed that she
OL,17,Fhad a condition called Spontaneous
OL,18,FIntracranial Hypotension (SIH) which
OL,19,Frequired a fluid injection into her
OL,20,Fback to cure it.
