OL,3,CEx-patient of Michael Watt to receive
OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,FShe claimed there was no discussion
OL,7,Fabout the risks associated with the
OL,8,Fprocedure or any alternative diagnosis.
OL,10,FIn November 2016, Ms Norney attended
OL,11,Fhospital to have the blood patch
OL,12,Fperformed by the neurologist.
OL,14,FWatt came into the cubicle in his
OL,15,Feveryday clothes, unmasked and not
OL,16,Fwearing gloves, according to her
OL,17,Faccount.
OL,19,FShe also remained in normal clothing
OL,20,Fwhen told to lie face down on the bed
OL,21,Fso he could carry out the injection.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
