OL,6,FAt one point she felt severe pain in
OL,7,Fher right leg and asked him to stop,
OL,8,Fbut he continued and said "just a bit
OL,9,Fmore".
OL,11,FShe described the pain as excruciating
OL,12,Fand that it felt like her leg was
OL,13,Fgoing to burst.
OL,15,FWhen the procedure ended she was
OL,16,Fadvised to stay prone for up to 10
OL,17,Fminutes before leaving.
OL,19,FMs Norney claimed that by the time she
OL,20,Fgot up Watt and an accompanying nurse
OL,21,Fhad already gone.
