OL,6,FShe described feeling soreness in her
OL,7,Fback and leg, but said she was not
OL,8,Fprovided with any help, guidance or
OL,9,Fappointment for a review.
OL,11,FNo statement or evidence was provided
OL,12,Fby Watt as part of his defence to the
OL,13,Faction.
OL,15,FMr Justice Colton described the
OL,16,Fneurologist's written records of what
OL,17,Ftook place as "woefully inadequate and
OL,18,Fsubstandard".
