OL,6,FNegligence was established against the
OL,7,Fstruck-off doctor over his
OL,8,Fconsultation with Ms Norney and
OL,9,Fdiagnosis that she was suffering from
OL,10,FSIH.
OL,12,F"This negligent diagnosis was
OL,13,Fcompounded by other actions of (Mr
OL,14,FWatt), including his failure to
OL,15,Fconduct a neurological examination,
OL,16,Fhis failure to obtain informed consent
OL,17,Fand his failure to consider
OL,18,Falternative approaches," the judge
OL,19,Fsaid.
