OL,6,FDealing with the procedure carried out
OL,7,Fin November 2016, a litany of
OL,8,Funacceptable behaviour highlighted by
OL,9,Fa consultant anaesthetist witness
OL,10,Fincluded:
OL,12,F- Failures to obtain informed consent
OL,13,For carry out proper pre-procedure
OL,14,Fpreparation.
OL,16,F- Ms Norney remained in her outdoor
OL,17,Fclothes but should have been dressed
OL,18,Fin a hospital gown.
