OL,4,C#50,000 in damages, judge rules
OL,6,F- The cubicle was an inappropriate
OL,7,Farea for the performance of an
OL,8,Finvasive procedure and should have
OL,9,Fcontained resuscitation equipment.
OL,11,F- Watt should have, at the very
OL,12,Fminimum, worn gloves, a mask and
OL,13,Fdressed in surgical scrubs due to
OL,14,Frisks of introducing infection.
OL,16,F- Watt persisted beyond Ms Norney's
OL,17,Fcomplaints of pain and discomfort.
